Brierley Investments Overseas NV isissuing a 100 mln dlr eurobond due April 30, 1992 paying 8-1/4pct and priced at par, lead manager Banque Paribas CapitalMarkets said.    The non-callable bond is available in denominations of5,000 dlrs and will be listed in Luxembourg.    The selling concession is 1-1/4 pct while management andunderwriting combined pays 5/8 pct.    The issue is guaranteed by Brierley Investments Ltd.Payment date is April 30. REUTER&#3;